<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(١٨٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَمَرَّتْ بِهِ}</span> ... قَامَتْ بِهِ، وَقَعَدَتْ؛ لِخِفَّةِ الْحَمْلِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(١٨٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَثْقَلَتْ}</span> ... صَارَتْ ثَقِيلَةً لِأَجْلِ الْحَمْلِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(١٩٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَتَعَالَى}</span> ... تَعَاظَمَ، وَتَنَزَّهَ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(١٩٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{تُنظِرُونِ}</span> ... تُمْهِلُونِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(١٩٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَلِيِّيَ}</span> ... نَاصِرِي، وَحَافِظِي مِنْ كُلِّ سُوءٍ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(١٩٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{خُذِ الْعَفْوَ}</span> ... خُذْ مَا تَيَسَّرَ مِنْ أَخْلَاقِ النَّاسِ، وَلَا تُكَلِّفْهُمْ مَا لَا يُرِيدُونَ بَذْلَهُ لَكَ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(١٩٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بِالْعُرْفِ}</span> ... بِالْمَعْرُوفِ، وَهُوَ كُلُّ قَوْلٍ وَعَمَلٍ حَسَنٍ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(١٩٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْجَاهِلِينَ}</span> ... السُّفَهَاءِ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٢٠٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَنزَغَنَّكَ}</span> ... يُصِيبَنَّكَ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٢٠٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{نَزْغٌ}</span> ... وَسْوَسَةٌ، وَتَثْبِيطٌ عَنِ الْخَيْرِ، وَحَثٌّ عَلَى الشَّرِّ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٢٠٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَاسْتَعِذْ بِاللهِ}</span> ... فَالْجَا مُسْتَجِيرًا بِاللهِ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(٢٠١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{طَائِفٌ مِّنَ الشَّيْطَانِ}</span> ... عَارِضٌ مِنْ وَسْوَسَةِ الشَّيْطَانِ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(٢٠٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَمُدُّونَهُمْ}</span> ... يُعِينُونَهُمْ فِي الْغَوَايَةِ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(٢٠٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لَا يُقْصِرُونَ}</span> ... لَا يَدَّخِرُونَ وُسْعًا فِي غَوَايَتِهِمْ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(٢٠٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{اجْتَبَيْتَهَا}</span> ... اخْتَلَقْتَهَا وَأَحْدَثْتَهَا.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c2">(٢٠٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بَصَائِرُ}</span> ... حُجَجٌ، وَبَرَاهِينُ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>